lead_paragraph: Trea Turner hit his second home run of the game with two outs in the bottom of the ninth, a solo shot that gave the Washington Nationals a 5-4 victory over the Philadelphia Phillies on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Turner's HR Gives Nationals 5-4 Victory Over Phillies
